 \lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{e^{x/n}}{n} 
 \begin{align} \lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{e^{x/n}}{n}  &= \left(\lim_{n\to\infty} e^{x/n}\right)\left(\lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{1}{n}\right)\\ &= (1)(0)\\ &= 0 \end{align} 
